当我身处险境，
When I was out there,

00:07:29.630 --> 00:07:33.020
大海抱我在怀里，
the ocean would hold me,

00:07:33.020 --> 00:07:36.364
拍打我、摇晃我，
rock me and throw me,

00:07:36.364 --> 00:07:39.684
像在婴儿床里。
light as a child.

00:07:39.684 --> 00:07:43.121
但我如此疲惫，
But now I'm so heavy,

00:07:43.121 --> 00:07:46.325
谁能给我慰藉。
nothing consoles me.

00:07:46.325 --> 00:07:49.761
我心如漂流木，
My mind floats like driftwood,

00:07:49.761 --> 00:07:53.035
狂野，任性，无助。
wayward and wild.

